data.description: Awesome location and neighborhood! 3 Bedrooms overlooking gorgeous backyard on ravine with creek.  Total privacy with wooded backdrop.  Private screened in porch off living room. 2 wood burning fireplaces. Finished walk-out basement with bar. New roof, less than one year old.  Newer furnace.  New laminate flooring throughout upstairs, and original hardwood floors in bedrooms.  Custom fit Levolor wood blinds and Bali shades. Brand new ceiling fans in all upstairs rooms. Pella Windows. Heavily insulated attic with good storage space. Large fire pit area that can accommodate large gatherings of 15 people or more.  The perfect location for for family get-togethers and celebrations in a quiet and peaceful neighborhood.  BRILLIANT Autumn colors!  Jane Addams school district.
